==Notes==
*Located northwest of [[Wrong]] and north of the Shrine of Compassion. 
*Receives the 50% Dungeon Skill Gain Bonus.
==[[Champion Spawns]]==
Beware adventurers, within this frozen cave the [[Champion_Spawns#Queen_of_the_Snow_-_Ice_Witch|Queen of the Snow - Ice Witch]] reigns! She is one of the many [[Champion_Spawns|Champions]] that inhabit the lands of Sosaria.

*white drake - Level 2b
